## Context

- All 5 Phase 1 development tasks complete for ts-striatal-interneuron-pathology
- **Task 588**: Project scaffold verified — config.py, pipeline.py, download.py, __init__.py all in place. Dependencies: scanpy, anndata, harmonypy, scrublet, leidenalg, pydeseq2.
